Individual




Stephen R. Avera



Mr. Stephen R. Avera is Secretary, Executive VP & General Counsel at Flowers Foods, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Tasty Baking Co. Mr. Avera was previously employed as Vice President & General Counsel by Flowers Foods Bakeries Group LLC and Assistant General Counsel & Associate by Flowers Industries, Inc.



