Executive Profile
Stephen R. Avera  Executive Vice President, General Counsel and Secretary, Flowers Foods, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships60$1,325,552As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Stephen R. Avera has been an Executive Vice President of Flowers Foods, Inc. since May 2008 and has been its Secretary and General Counsel since February 2002. Mr. Avera is responsible for all the legal affairs of Flowers Foods. In addition, he also has responsibility for Flowers Foods Inc.'s governmental affairs. He served as Senior Vice President of Flowers Foods Inc., from September 8, 2004 to May 2008. He served as Associate and Assistant General counsel of Flowers ... Industries from February 1986 to July 1998. He joined Flowers Foods' predecessor, Flowers Industries, in 1986 as an Associate and Assistant General Counsel. He has four-year legal career as a Captain in the U.S. Army Judge Advocate General's Corps. He served as Vice President and General Counsel of Flowers Bakeries, LLC from July 1998 to February 2002. In 2001, he took on the additional responsibilities of general counsel for Flowers' frozen and specialty operation. Mr. Avera has been a Director of Tasty Baking Company since May 20, 2011. He is a Member of the State Bars of Alabama, Georgia and Florida and a member of the American Corporate Counsel Association. Mr. Avera holds a Bachelor's Degree and a Juris Doctor Degree from the University of Alabama in Tuscaloosa.Read Full Background




