Stephen R. Avera 
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President Secretary and General Counsel at FLOWERS FOODS INC, Stephen R. Avera  made $1,305,911 in total compensation.  Of this total $471,539 was received as a salary, $161,078 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $637,870 was awarded as stock and $35,424 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


